main event: A UFO sighting was reported near Cape Canaveral, Florida and Cuba on 23 August 1961 shortly after a missile launch.
interesting points: The object was described as circular and white, with the same magnitude as Venus or Echo 1., The observers included military personnel and civilians, some of whom reported the object as being 30-40 degrees above the horizon., No sound was heard during the sighting, indicating it was likely not an aircraft., The sightings coincided with the launch of a ranger satellite, leading to speculation about the object being associated with the missile activity., Multiple witnesses stated they saw the object disappear slowly, with one describing a 'shock wave' visible from the object's nose.
